</figure>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06025001">
<title>
General Notes
</title>
<ptxt>
Roof carrier brackets are to be reused.
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06025002">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots and remove 4 roof carrier brackets and roof panel.
</ptxt>
</s1>
