<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A9B06025003">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Before conducting any weld, check installation position and condition for installation part(s). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B04005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A9B04008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct tack welding to roof panel center No. 2 member (without sun roof model only), roof panel center No. 3 member and roof panel center No.4 member.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply body sealer to roof front inner rail, roof panel center No. 2 member (without sun roof model only), roof panel center No.1 member (without sun roof model only), sliding roof reinforcement (with sun roof model only), roof panel center No.3 member, roof panel center No.4 member and roof back inner member.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0179.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "204.967mm" ver = "04" gw = "426" gh = "564"/>
<callout>
